description: Strating from Hotel Chanteclerc Parking, we follow #1 Trail. Got to the top where an old shack is there, very usefull in winter. On the end of september it is colorful.  Have a nice trip.
directions: From Montreal, take the #15 road to Chanteclerc Hotel at Ste-Adele.
title: Mont Loup-Garou Q.C.
